Cool, now, stand up for a second, and do a little 1-2 step jig to the beat here. Yeah, a little back an fourth. Yeah, like that!  Now, try closing your eyes while your dancing, now start smiling just because,  and remember how wonderful life can feel!!

The Power Of The Universe, the Eternal Presence, Flows WITHIN YOU! It's happening for me, so it can definitely happen for you!  

No go out there and have the most Wonderful Life Heroes, it's so worth it! There is no problem you can't handle, there is no challenge you can't rise to, you are CHAMPIONS!!! :D :D :D

Love you all, GOOD LUCK HEROES!!

8 Bit Passion!

Greetings Heroes! 

Today I'd like to talk (or rant lol)  to you about PASSION!  Finding your passion is what life is all about, so how do you go about finding it??  :O

It's the feeling inside of you that wants to get out, but it requires that you align your life with the present moment! 

But what is Presence? Some have said To be the only real thing, the light of consciousness itself!

All things are contained within THIS MOMENT. It's has been said that there is no past or future, they are, in a way, an illusion! Turns out,  there is only ever NOW.  The past occurred as the present, and any future happening will only come into existence as the present. 

To become one with the Present Moment, become aligned with what you are doing right... NOW.   

Feel this moment, get in touch with it. ENGAGE IT FULLY.  here's a quote from the spiritual teacher, Eckhart Tolle:

"There is always this one step, and so you give it your fullest attention.  This doesn't mean that you don't know where you're going, this just means that the step that you're taking right now is PRIMARY, the destination is SECONDARY, and what you encounter at your destination once you get there, depends on the quality of this one step." - Eckhart Tolle

Here is one from Oprah (i didn't realize how cool she was until recently!):

"Whatever you're doing in any given moment, if you do it your best, it leads you to the BEST NEXT MOMENT." - Oprah

So you don't have to worry about what's coming. So long as you are always doing your best in THIS MOMENT, the "what's coming" will always be as awesome as it can possibly be! :D

"Be the Hero of your own movie." - Joe Rogan

When you do your best in this moment, as in being present in this moment(yes those are the same!), then just surrender to it and ACCEPT the path in front of you, because it's always the best possible path forward!!  No need to worry about all the other stuff, that's just in the way! :D 

Bringing it back to Passion now, when you are taking your best action in the present moment, you will find that the best decision in any moment is the one that resonates with you instinctually. So as long as you are in this moment, you will be true to yourself, and by being the natural you, you will discover your passion!  Because passion exists only in the present! 

It's hard to describe what is inherently indescribable, but I hope some of that made sense! Lol! 

Close your eyes, and FEEL THE PRESENT MOMENT!, by doing this, your Passion will SHINE THROUGH!

That's it for now, GOOD LUCK HEROES!!  (and happy holidays! :D)

Heroes! We got our mystery man cornered in the dockside warehouse, and finally we'll figure out who it was that sabotaged our attempt to expose the Emperor, before it's too late!  : o

(a cloaked figure, moves quickly in the darkness)

"You there, stop!" 

(Your teammate's magic light shines on them through the darkness, The clocked figure stops, and turns to you, ) 

"It's over!" you exclaim, "Now remove your hood, and show us who you are!"

(the figure removes his hood, and to your SHOCK you discover that it is your long lost FRIEND, who you started this adventure with!  He had disappeared during your escape from the Emperor's Club!  Now HERE HE IS, WORKING AGAINST US???  : O   )

"Traitors…" He snarls, eyes fixed on you. "How DARE you defy the EMPEROR! Have you no respect for the POWER of DESTINY?"

"It is you," you respond "who does not understand the DESTINY OF POWER." 

"The people WANT him to rule over them, and we were all meant to SERVE the great emperor!!  How do you not UNDERSTAND?? He knows the SECRET OF THE UNIVERSE! Now once he controls the POWER OF THE EARTH, then he will take control of all and cleanse these lands of all he deems UNWORTHY and we will FINALLY prosper and thrive under his great leadership, the ALL POWERFUL ONE!!

"My friend, " you calmly respond. "When will you learn that TRUE POWER DOES NOT TAKE, TRUE POWER GIVES." Please, come with us" 

"FOOL!" he fires, "How DARE you lecture ME!  You will NEVER understand what I've had to go through, to lose EVERYTHING!!!"  
(his eyes lost in mad thought, tears begin running down his face...he lives in a WAKING NIGHTMARE...)

"…he promised….HE PROMISED TO MAKE IT BETTER!! .  …he WILL make it all better, but you so called "Heroes" are in the way…".   

"The Emperor, showed ME, the TRUTH, he showed me the SECRET OF THE UNIVERSE, AND THE GREAT POWER, THE POWER OF DESTINY!!!  and now... I will show YOU!!!

(a chilling swell of energy pulls the light from the room…circling our new foe) 

"HA.. HA.. Haaaaa….Now you will see.." he says. " ….NOW… YOU WILL SEE…. THE POWER OF THE EMPEROR!!" 

****CRRRRRAAAAACCCCKKKK!!*** ( A MASSIVE SURGE OF ENERGY ERUPTS FROM WITHIN OUR OPPONENT, HE CRACKLES WITH A DARK ENERGY…the room WARPS into an ALTERNATE DIMENSION!!) 

...Your friend is lost in his nightmare, but is there time to save him?

"My friend…" 

(You close your eyes, absorbing the pain, then transmuting the pain into LOVE, your opponent sprints at you with hatred in his eyes! You are no longer looking at your friend, you are now looking, at an ANTI-HERO)

" COME AND SEE 'HEROES', He screams!!  COME AND SEE!!!!!" 

(You move into position, fix your gaze, you focus your breath... leave your thoughts and become your true self ...you are ready...)

...AND SO THE FIGHT BEGINS!!!!

GOOD LUCK HEROES!!!

snippet.description:
Challenge accepted! Please, subscribe to collaborate even more with new videos.

For those who did not understand what is going on this video, here's a brief explanation: The main loud music really comes from the tesla coil sparks. They are literally playing the music due to the programmed phase, pulse width and firing frequency! So, there are no speakers, no audio / video special effects. It looks even better in person and sounds almost the same, just without the beat / percussion backing track. 

I hope you all enjoy this version where I worked for musical tesla coils!

title: Bohemian Rhapsody Meets Singing Tesla Coils

snippet.title: Bohemian Rhapsody Meets Singing Tesla Coils
snippet.description:
Challenge accepted! Please, SUBSCRIBE to collaborate even more with new videos! 

Just worked hard on this song. I composed each coil channel listening to the studio and Live at Rock Montreal, 1981 version. Mercury meets tesla, mustache power?

For those who did not understand what is going on this video, here's a brief explanation: The main loud music really comes from the tesla coil sparks. They are literally playing the music due to the programmed phase, pulse width and firing frequency! So, there are no speakers, no audio / video special effects. It looks even better in person and sounds almost the same, just without the beat / percussion backing track. 

I hope you all enjoy this version where I worked for musical tesla coils! 

Any question? feel free to comment on.

#bohemianrhapsody #teslacoil #franzolielectronics

title: Sweet Dreams Are Made of TESLA COILS

snippet.title: Sweet Dreams Are Made of TESLA COILS
snippet.description:
Eurythmics - Sweet Dreams (Are Made of This) performed by musical tesla coil quartet!
Note: The loud music actually comes from the sparks from the tesla coil. It's literally playing the music due to the programmed phase, pulse width and trigger frequency! So there are no speakers, no audio / video special effects. Just the drum backing track that is not played by the tesla coils. It looks even better in person and sounds almost the same, just louder than people expect.

Any question? feel free to comment on.

title: Don't Stop Believin' - Journey Piano Cover

snippet.title: Don't Stop Believin' - Journey Piano Cover
snippet.description:
Time to switch things up a bit with Journey's classic hit in 1981 from the album Escape. I could play it anywhere and listeners light up and sing along when they hear it. What do you all think of this change of pace? Every now and then I hope deviate and do covers from other genres. Love the message of the song, and I hope it resonates with you all! The best is yet to come; don't stop believing:)

Based off of Mr. Arranger Man's cover, which can be found here: https://musescore.com/user/36070839/scores/6594715

Subscribe for weekly uploads. What cover should I do next?
